<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en" class="scroll-smooth">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Muhamad Gilang Fikri Azi � Portfolio</title>
    <script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com"></script>
    <script defer src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/alpinejs@3.x.x/dist/cdn.min.js"></script>
    <style>
        html { scroll-behavior: smooth; }
        body { font-family: 'Inter', system-ui, -apple-system, sans-serif; }
        @keyframes float { 0%,100%{transform:translateY(0)} 50%{transform:translateY(-10px)} }
        .float { animation: float 3s ease-in-out infinite; }
        @keyframes fadeInUp { from{opacity:0;transform:translateY(30px)} to{opacity:1;transform:translateY(0)} }
        .fade-in { animation: fadeInUp 0.6s ease-out forwards; }
        .fade-in-delay-1 { animation-delay: 0.2s; opacity: 0; }
        .fade-in-delay-2 { animation-delay: 0.4s; opacity: 0; }
        .fade-in-delay-3 { animation-delay: 0.6s; opacity: 0; }
        .skill-card:hover .skill-icon { transform: scale(1.1) rotate(-5deg); }
        .skill-icon { transition: all 0.3s ease; }
        .project-card { transition: all 0.3s ease; }
        .project-card:hover { transform: translateY(-5px); box-shadow: 0 20px 40px rgba(0,0,0,0.1); }
        .gradient-text { background: linear-gradient(135deg, #3b82f6, #8b5cf6, #06b6d4); -webkit-background-clip: text; -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent; background-clip: text; }
        .btn-primary { background: linear-gradient(135deg, #3b82f6, #2563eb); transition: all 0.3s ease; }
        .btn-primary:hover { background: linear-gradient(135deg, #2563eb, #1d4ed8); transform: translateY(-2px); box-shadow: 0 10px 25px -5px rgba(59,130,246,0.4); }
        .timeline-dot { box-shadow: 0 0 0 4px rgba(59,130,246,0.2); }
    </style>
</head>
<body x-data="{ mobileOpen: false }">    <!-- NAVBAR -->
    <nav x-data="{ scrolled: false }"
         x-init="window.addEventListener('scroll', () => scrolled = window.scrollY > 30)"
         :class="scrolled ? 'bg-white/90 backdrop-blur-md shadow-sm' : 'bg-transparent'"
         class="fixed top-0 left-0 right-0 z-50 transition-all duration-300 px-6">
        <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto flex items-center justify-between h-16 md:h-20">
            <a href="#" class="text-xl font-bold">
                <span :class="scrolled ? 'text-gray-800' : 'text-white'" class="transition-colors">Gilang<span class="text-blue-500">.</span></span>
            </a>
            <div class="hidden md:flex items-center gap-8">
                <a href="#about" :class="scrolled ? 'text-gray-600 hover:text-blue-600' : 'text-gray-200 hover:text-white'" class="text-sm font-medium transition">About</a>
                <a href="#skills" :class="scrolled ? 'text-gray-600 hover:text-blue-600' : 'text-gray-200 hover:text-white'" class="text-sm font-medium transition">Skills</a>
                <a href="#experience" :class="scrolled ? 'text-gray-600 hover:text-blue-600' : 'text-gray-200 hover:text-white'" class="text-sm font-medium transition">Experience</a>
                <a href="#projects" :class="scrolled ? 'text-gray-600 hover:text-blue-600' : 'text-gray-200 hover:text-white'" class="text-sm font-medium transition">Projects</a>
                <a href="#contact" class="btn-primary text-white text-sm font-semibold px-5 py-2.5 rounded-xl">Contact</a>
            </div>
            <button @click="mobileOpen = !mobileOpen" :class="scrolled ? 'text-gray-700' : 'text-white'" class="md:hidden p-2">
                <svg x-show="!mobileOpen" class="w-6 h-6" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M4 6h16M4 12h16M4 18h16"/></svg>
                <svg x-show="mobileOpen" class="w-6 h-6" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" style="display:none"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M6 18L18 6M6 6l12 12"/></svg>
            </button>
        </div>
        <div x-show="mobileOpen" x-cloak class="md:hidden bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-xl border border-gray-100 overflow-hidden"
             x-transition:enter="transition ease-out duration-200"
             x-transition:enter-start="opacity-0 -translate-y-4"
             x-transition:enter-end="opacity-100 translate-y-0">
            <div class="py-3">
                <a href="#about" @click="mobileOpen = false" class="block px-5 py-3 text-sm font-medium text-gray-700 hover:bg-blue-50">About</a>
                <a href="#skills" @click="mobileOpen = false" class="block px-5 py-3 text-sm font-medium text-gray-700 hover:bg-blue-50">Skills</a>
                <a href="#experience" @click="mobileOpen = false" class="block px-5 py-3 text-sm font-medium text-gray-700 hover:bg-blue-50">Experience</a>
                <a href="#projects" @click="mobileOpen = false" class="block px-5 py-3 text-sm font-medium text-gray-700 hover:bg-blue-50">Projects</a>
                <a href="#contact" @click="mobileOpen = false" class="block mx-3 mt-2 px-5 py-3 text-sm font-medium text-white bg-blue-600 rounded-xl text-center">Contact</a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </nav>

    <!-- HERO -->
    <section class="relative min-h-screen flex items-center bg-gradient-to-br from-slate-900 via-blue-950 to-slate-900 overflow-hidden">
        <div class="absolute inset-0 overflow-hidden opacity-20">
            <div class="absolute top-1/4 left-1/4 w-72 h-72 bg-blue-500 rounded-full blur-[100px]"></div>
            <div class="absolute bottom-1/4 right-1/4 w-96 h-96 bg-purple-500 rounded-full blur-[120px]"></div>
        </div>
        <div class="relative max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6 py-32 md:py-40 w-full">
            <div class="max-w-3xl">
                <div class="fade-in fade-in-delay-1 inline-flex items-center gap-2 bg-white/10 backdrop-blur-sm rounded-full px-4 py-1.5 text-sm text-blue-200 border border-white/10 mb-6">
                    <span class="w-2 h-2 bg-green-400 rounded-full animate-pulse"></span>
                    Available for opportunities
                </div>
                <h1 class="fade-in fade-in-delay-1 text-4xl md:text-6xl lg:text-7xl font-bold text-white leading-tight">
                    Hi, I'm <span class="gradient-text">Gilang</span>
                </h1>
                <p class="fade-in fade-in-delay-2 text-xl md:text-2xl text-blue-200 mt-4 font-light">
                    Software Developer with <span class="text-white font-semibold">5 years</span> of experience
                </p>
                <p class="fade-in fade-in-delay-2 text-gray-400 mt-3 max-w-xl">
                    Crafting robust backend systems and engaging frontend experiences &mdash; from .NET and Laravel to Angular and Tailwind.
                </p>
                <div class="fade-in fade-in-delay-3 flex flex-wrap gap-4 mt-8">
                    <a href="#projects" class="btn-primary text-white font-semibold px-6 py-3 rounded-xl inline-flex items-center gap-2">
                        <svg class="w-5 h-5" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 11H5m14 0l-6-6m6 6l-6 6"/></svg>
                        View My Work
                    </a>
                    <a href="#contact" class="bg-white/10 backdrop-blur-sm border border-white/20 text-white font-semibold px-6 py-3 rounded-xl hover:bg-white/20 transition inline-flex items-center gap-2">
                        <svg class="w-5 h-5" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M3 8l7.89 5.26a2 2 0 002.22 0L21 8M5 19h14a2 2 0 002-2V7a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v10a2 2 0 002 2z"/></svg>
                        Contact Me
                    </a>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="absolute bottom-8 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 float">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-white/40" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 14l-7 7m0 0l-7-7m7 7V3"/></svg>
        </div>
    </section>    <!-- ABOUT -->
    <section id="about" class="py-20 md:py-28 bg-white">
        <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6">
            <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center">
                <div>
                    <span class="text-blue-600 font-semibold text-sm tracking-wider uppercase">About Me</span>
                    <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-gray-900 mt-2">Passionate <span class="gradient-text">Full Stack</span> Developer</h2>
                    <div class="w-20 h-1 bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-500 to-cyan-500 rounded-full mt-4 mb-6"></div>
                    <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed mb-4">
                        Software Developer with approximately <strong class="text-gray-800">5 years</strong> of experience, specializing in building enterprise-scale applications using microservices architecture. Currently working as
                        <strong class="text-gray-800">IT Full Stack Engineer at Manulife</strong>. Previously served as
                        <strong class="text-gray-800">Senior Developer at PT Adicipta Inovasi Teknologi</strong>,
                        <strong class="text-gray-800">Software Developer at Bank OCBC NISP</strong>,
                        <strong class="text-gray-800">Web Developer at Morning Glory Enterprise</strong>, and
                        <strong class="text-gray-800">Junior Backend Developer at PT Drago Kreatifindo</strong>.
                    </p>
                    <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed mb-6">
                        Proficient in backend development with <strong>.NET (C#, VB), Laravel, CodeIgniter</strong>, and modern frontend with <strong>Angular, JavaScript, TypeScript</strong>. Experienced with <strong>Apache Kafka, RabbitMQ</strong> for message brokering and <strong>Camunda</strong> for business process automation. Skilled in <strong>PostgreSQL, SQL Server, MySQL, Oracle</strong> for database management. Comfortable with <strong>microservices architecture</strong> and third-party system integrations in large-scale national projects.
                    </p>
                    <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-4">
                        <div class="bg-blue-50 rounded-xl px-4 py-3 text-center min-w-[100px]">
                            <div class="text-2xl font-bold text-blue-600">5</div>
                            <div class="text-xs text-gray-500">Years Exp</div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="bg-purple-50 rounded-xl px-4 py-3 text-center min-w-[100px]">
                            <div class="text-2xl font-bold text-purple-600">5</div>
                            <div class="text-xs text-gray-500">Companies</div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="bg-orange-50 rounded-xl px-4 py-3 text-center min-w-[100px]">
                            <div class="text-2xl font-bold text-orange-600">15+</div>
                            <div class="text-xs text-gray-500">Projects</div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="bg-cyan-50 rounded-xl px-4 py-3 text-center min-w-[100px]">
                            <div class="text-2xl font-bold text-cyan-600">10+</div>
                            <div class="text-xs text-gray-500">Projects</div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="flex justify-center">
                    <div class="relative">
                        <div class="w-64 h-64 md:w-80 md:h-80 bg-gradient-to-br from-blue-400 to-purple-500 rounded-3xl rotate-6 absolute inset-0 opacity-20 blur-sm"></div>
                        <div class="w-64 h-64 md:w-80 md:h-80 bg-gradient-to-br from-blue-50 to-gray-100 rounded-3xl flex items-center justify-center border-2 border-gray-200 relative">
                            <span class="text-7xl">&#x1F468;&#x200D;&#x1F4BB;</span>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- SKILLS -->
    <section id="skills" class="py-20 md:py-28 bg-gray-50">
        <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6">
            <div class="text-center max-w-2xl mx-auto mb-14">
                <span class="text-blue-600 font-semibold text-sm tracking-wider uppercase">Skills</span>
                <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-gray-900 mt-2">Tech Stack</h2>
                <p class="text-gray-500 mt-3">Technologies I work with on a daily basis</p>
            </div>
            <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
                <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-6 shadow-sm border border-gray-100 hover:shadow-md transition skill-card">
                    <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-6">
                        <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-blue-100 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center skill-icon">
                            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-blue-600" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M10 20l4-16m4 4l4 4-4 4M6 16l-4-4 4-4"/></svg>
                        </div>
                        <h3 class="font-bold text-gray-800 text-lg">Backend</h3>
                    </div>
                    <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2">
                        <span class="bg-blue-50 text-blue-700 text-sm font-medium px-3 py-1.5 rounded-lg">.NET</span>
                        <span class="bg-indigo-50 text-indigo-700 text-sm font-medium px-3 py-1.5 rounded-lg">VB</span>
                        <span class="bg-red-50 text-red-700 text-sm font-medium px-3 py-1.5 rounded-lg">Laravel</span>
                        <span class="bg-orange-50 text-orange-700 text-sm font-medium px-3 py-1.5 rounded-lg">CodeIgniter</span>
                        <span class="bg-green-50 text-green-700 text-sm font-medium px-3 py-1.5 rounded-lg">REST API</span>
                        <span class="bg-cyan-50 text-cyan-700 text-sm font-medium px-3 py-1.5 rounded-lg">Microservices</span>
                        <span class="bg-purple-50 text-purple-700 text-sm font-medium px-3 py-1.5 rounded-lg">PostgreSQL</span>
                        <span class="bg-yellow-50 text-yellow-700 text-sm font-medium px-3 py-1.5 rounded-lg">MySQL</span>
                        <span class="bg-teal-50 text-teal-700 text-sm font-medium px-3 py-1.5 rounded-lg">SQL Server</span>
                        <span class="bg-red-100 text-red-700 text-sm font-medium px-3 py-1.5 rounded-lg">Oracle</span>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-6 shadow-sm border border-gray-100 hover:shadow-md transition skill-card">
                    <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-6">
                        <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-purple-100 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center skill-icon">
                            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-purple-600" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9.75 17L9 20l-1 1h8l-1-1-.75-3M3 13h18M5 17h14a2 2 0 002-2V5a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v10a2 2 0 002 2z"/></svg>
                        </div>
                        <h3 class="font-bold text-gray-800 text-lg">Frontend</h3>
                    </div>
                    <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2">
                        <span class="bg-red-50 text-red-700 text-sm font-medium px-3 py-1.5 rounded-lg">Angular</span>
                        <span class="bg-blue-50 text-blue-700 text-sm font-medium px-3 py-1.5 rounded-lg">TypeScript</span>
                        <span class="bg-yellow-50 text-yellow-700 text-sm font-medium px-3 py-1.5 rounded-lg">JavaScript</span>
                        <span class="bg-blue-50 text-blue-700 text-sm font-medium px-3 py-1.5 rounded-lg">Tailwind CSS</span>
                        <span class="bg-purple-50 text-purple-700 text-sm font-medium px-3 py-1.5 rounded-lg">Bootstrap</span>
                        <span class="bg-cyan-50 text-cyan-700 text-sm font-medium px-3 py-1.5 rounded-lg">Alpine.js</span>
                        <span class="bg-orange-50 text-orange-700 text-sm font-medium px-3 py-1.5 rounded-lg">jQuery</span>
                        <span class="bg-green-50 text-green-700 text-sm font-medium px-3 py-1.5 rounded-lg">Blade</span>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-6 shadow-sm border border-gray-100 hover:shadow-md transition skill-card">
                    <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-6">
                        <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-emerald-100 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center skill-icon">
                            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-emerald-600" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M10.325 4.317c.426-1.756 2.924-1.756 3.35 0a1.724 1.724 0 002.573 1.066c1.543-.94 3.31.826 2.37 2.37a1.724 1.724 0 001.066 2.573c1.756.426 1.756 2.924 0 3.35a1.724 1.724 0 00-1.066 2.573c.94 1.543-.826 3.31-2.37 2.37a1.724 1.724 0 00-2.573 1.066c-.426 1.756-2.924 1.756-3.35 0a1.724 1.724 0 00-2.573-1.066c-1.543.94-3.31-.826-2.37-2.37a1.724 1.724 0 00-1.066-2.573c-1.756-.426-1.756-2.924 0-3.35a1.724 1.724 0 001.066-2.573c-.94-1.543.826-3.31 2.37-2.37.996.608 2.296.07 2.572-1.065z"/><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M15 12a3 3 0 11-6 0 3 3 0 016 0z"/></svg>
                        </div>
                        <h3 class="font-bold text-gray-800 text-lg">Tools</h3>
                    </div>
                    <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2">
                        <span class="bg-gray-100 text-gray-700 text-sm font-medium px-3 py-1.5 rounded-lg">Docker</span>
                        <span class="bg-gray-100 text-gray-700 text-sm font-medium px-3 py-1.5 rounded-lg">Git</span>
                        <span class="bg-gray-100 text-gray-700 text-sm font-medium px-3 py-1.5 rounded-lg">Linux</span>
                        <span class="bg-gray-100 text-gray-700 text-sm font-medium px-3 py-1.5 rounded-lg">PgAdmin</span>
                        <span class="bg-gray-100 text-gray-700 text-sm font-medium px-3 py-1.5 rounded-lg">Cloudflare</span>
                        <span class="bg-orange-100 text-orange-700 text-sm font-medium px-3 py-1.5 rounded-lg">Kafka</span>
                        <span class="bg-amber-100 text-amber-700 text-sm font-medium px-3 py-1.5 rounded-lg">RabbitMQ</span>
                        <span class="bg-rose-100 text-rose-700 text-sm font-medium px-3 py-1.5 rounded-lg">Camunda</span>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>    <!-- EXPERIENCE -->
    <section id="experience" class="py-20 md:py-28 bg-white">
        <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6">
            <div class="text-center max-w-2xl mx-auto mb-14">
                <span class="text-blue-600 font-semibold text-sm tracking-wider uppercase">Experience</span>
                <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-gray-900 mt-2">Work History</h2>
                <p class="text-gray-500 mt-3">My professional journey</p>
            </div>
            <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto space-y-8">
                <div class="relative pl-8 border-l-2 border-blue-200">
                    <div class="absolute -left-[9px] top-0 w-4 h-4 bg-blue-600 rounded-full timeline-dot"></div>
                    <div class="bg-gray-50 rounded-xl p-6 hover:shadow-sm transition">
                        <div class="flex items-start justify-between flex-wrap gap-2">
                            <div>
                                <h3 class="font-bold text-gray-800 text-lg">IT Full Stack Engineer</h3>
                                <p class="text-blue-600 font-medium">Manulife</p>
                            </div>
                            <span class="text-sm text-gray-400 bg-white px-3 py-1 rounded-full border">Jul 2025 — Present</span>
                        </div>
                        <ul class="text-gray-500 text-sm mt-3 space-y-1.5 list-disc list-inside">
                            <li>Developed <strong>PDLINK Web Agent</strong> for Manulife's partner banks: <strong>DBS</strong> and <strong>Danamon</strong>.</li>
                            <li>Built using <strong>.NET (VB)</strong> for backend, <strong>Angular</strong> for frontend, and <strong>Oracle</strong> for database.</li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="relative pl-8 border-l-2 border-indigo-200">
                    <div class="absolute -left-[9px] top-0 w-4 h-4 bg-indigo-600 rounded-full timeline-dot"></div>
                    <div class="bg-gray-50 rounded-xl p-6 hover:shadow-sm transition">
                        <div class="flex items-start justify-between flex-wrap gap-2">
                            <div>
                                <h3 class="font-bold text-gray-800 text-lg">Senior Software Developer</h3>
                                <p class="text-indigo-600 font-medium">PT Adicipta Inovasi Teknologi (PT ADINS)</p>
                            </div>
                            <span class="text-sm text-gray-400 bg-white px-3 py-1 rounded-full border">Jun 2024 — Present</span>
                        </div>
                        <ul class="text-gray-500 text-sm mt-3 space-y-1.5 list-disc list-inside">
                            <li>Contributed to the <strong>Hyundai Capital</strong> project — delivered key modules: AMS (Asset Management System) & CMS (Collection Management System).</li>
                            <li>Supervised development processes, ensured milestones met on time with high-quality standards.</li>
                            <li>Utilized <strong>.NET</strong> for backend, <strong>Angular</strong> for frontend, and <strong>PostgreSQL</strong> for database management.</li>
                            <li>Implemented <strong>RabbitMQ</strong> for message queueing and <strong>Camunda</strong> for business process automation.</li>
                            <li>Integrated multiple third-party systems: Asuransi Sinarmas, KBRU (regional bank), PT Delima (fiduciary), and Softphone system.</li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="relative pl-8 border-l-2 border-purple-200">
                    <div class="absolute -left-[9px] top-0 w-4 h-4 bg-purple-600 rounded-full timeline-dot"></div>
                    <div class="bg-gray-50 rounded-xl p-6 hover:shadow-sm transition">
                        <div class="flex items-start justify-between flex-wrap gap-2">
                            <div>
                                <h3 class="font-bold text-gray-800 text-lg">Software Developer</h3>
                                <p class="text-purple-600 font-medium">Bank OCBC NISP</p>
                            </div>
                            <span class="text-sm text-gray-400 bg-white px-3 py-1 rounded-full border">May 2022 — May 2024</span>
                        </div>
                        <ul class="text-gray-500 text-sm mt-3 space-y-1.5 list-disc list-inside">
                            <li>Developed and enhanced <strong>6+ internal projects</strong> using <strong>microservices architecture</strong>.</li>
                            <li>Created test scenarios, conducted SIT, and led UAT to ensure features met business requirements.</li>
                            <li>Optimized SQL queries, debugged issues across dev and production, handled system integration between legacy and modern platforms.</li>
                            <li>Used <strong>.NET (C#, ASP.NET Core, Web API)</strong> for backend, <strong>Angular</strong> for frontend, <strong>SQL Server</strong> for database.</li>
                            <li>Worked with <strong>Apache Kafka</strong> as message broker for distributed systems & asynchronous communication.</li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="relative pl-8 border-l-2 border-amber-200">
                    <div class="absolute -left-[9px] top-0 w-4 h-4 bg-amber-600 rounded-full timeline-dot"></div>
                    <div class="bg-gray-50 rounded-xl p-6 hover:shadow-sm transition">
                        <div class="flex items-start justify-between flex-wrap gap-2">
                            <div>
                                <h3 class="font-bold text-gray-800 text-lg">Web Programmer</h3>
                                <p class="text-amber-600 font-medium">Morning Glory Enterprise</p>
                            </div>
                            <span class="text-sm text-gray-400 bg-white px-3 py-1 rounded-full border">Nov 2020 — Feb 2021</span>
                        </div>
                        <ul class="text-gray-500 text-sm mt-3 space-y-1.5 list-disc list-inside">
                            <li>Collaborated with team to test applications and refine functionality based on feedback.</li>
                            <li>Developed responsive front-end interfaces based on UI/UX designs.</li>
